" Size="8" Leading="9" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">This enactment amends the <I>Holidays Act</I> to make Remembrance Day a legal holiday and give it the same status as Canada Day.
