<br /></MarginalNote><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2"><change>(2) On Remembrance Day, the Canadian flag on the Peace Tower shall be lowered to half-mast.</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><MarginalNote>Coming into force
